sees: announcement 
---
does: pm hsctf to register
---
sees: hsctf pms user welcome

at game start time => hsctf messages stream 'game started!'

hsctf pm user instructions 
---
does: pm hsctf 'solved <challenge name> <challenge sol'n>'
---
sees: congratulations, new score, available challenges

sees: leader on stream

does: pm hsctf score
---
sees: score

does: pm hsctf 'challenges'
---
sees: available challenges

does: pm hsctf 'show me <challenge name>'
---
sees: <challenge name>, if challenge is available or solved

does: pm hsctf 'help'
---
sees: help text

does: pm hsctf <anything else>
---
sees: 'i didn't catch that'
